Mat Hoffman's PRO BMX
 
Год выпуска: 2001
Жанр: Sports
Разработчик: T.J. Deci
Издательство: All Game Guide
Платформа: PS
Носитель: 1CD
Язык интерфейса: RUS
Тип перевода: текст
Описание: Built on the same Neversoft game engine, Mat Hoffman's Pro BMX is designed do the same thing for stunt riding that Tony Hawk's Pro Skater does for skateboarding. Mat Hoffman's Pro BMX offers open, 3D environments, an intuitive trick system, and lots of options to allow players to customize their riders, develop skills, and design their own courses. Also following the lead of Tony Hawk's Pro Skater and its sequel, Mat Hoffman's Pro BMX boasts a modern "alternative" soundtrack to enhance the cultural authenticity of the experience